{"tid":1286554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠要對話就學趙紫揚","createTime":"2019-07-05T01:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T02:02:38.000Z","uid":60051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ae47e5acf0edbb572b0ebd3765fb925fe26fea","tid":1286554,"uid":60051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5bgjHAChQQU&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5bgjHAChQQU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=b15c517b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5bgjHAChQQU&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n〔影片內容〕1989年5月19日，中央電視台播出總書記趙紫陽到天安門廣場對學生的發言，陪同趙紫陽探望學生有當時任中共中央辦公廳主任的溫家寶；以及學生絕食的相關報導。<br />\n<br />\n5月19日凌晨，趙紫陽到天安門廣場慰問學生，含淚道歉：「同學們，我們來得挺晚了，對不起同學們。」由於趙態度誠懇，學生宣布停止絕食，改為靜坐。當時廣場上絕食和聲援的學生近20萬人。<br />\n<br />\n唔需要代表，唔需要大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1330f23888d0b3c8bc6c0306c41a8e0bcd1757b","tid":1286554,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73df31927d7175c3ae0e62e6cd0b3f9b79b81001","tid":1286554,"uid":260588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:54:47.000Z","msg":"之後趙紫陽就收皮了"},{"pid":"22afc8fb20fe1bfadc56e72836b69679739e5c12","tid":1286554,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73df31927d7175c3ae0e62e6cd0b3f9b79b81001","tid":1286554,"u